            <button type="button" class="btn" onclick="alert('Chá»n cÃ¡c Ä‘Æ¡n cáº§n gá»™p trÆ°á»›c khi dÃ¹ng chá»©c nÄƒng nÃ y.')"><i class="fa-regular fa-copy"></i> Gá»™p Ä‘Æ¡n</button>
            <a class="btn" href="/don-hang/export.csv"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-export"></i> Xuáº¥t file <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i></a>
